problem_data.title: Excel Sheet Column Title
problem_data.description:
Given an integer columnNumber, return its corresponding column title as it appears in an Excel sheet.

For example:
A -> 1
B -> 2
C -> 3
...
Z -> 26
AA -> 27
AB -> 28
...
